entries.title: Biden administration wants Supreme Court to end Title 42 — just not yet
entries.description: The administration seeks another pause — at least a week — in winding down the Trump-era border policy.

entries.title: Zelenskyy expected to visit Washington on Wednesday
entries.description: The trip would come days after Congress, in the early hours of Tuesday morning, unveiled a year-end spending bill including about $45 billion for Ukraine.

entries.title: Conservative youth group disses McDaniel in race for RNC chair
entries.description: Turning Point USA straw poll endorses Harmeet Dhillon over Ronna McDaniel by a wide margin.
